fee break with a nice French Cake. At night you are treated with are fined French / Italian cuisine with a continental buffet spiced with African influences. We pride ourselves with friendly staff and the practical touches that make being away from home easier, whether you book our rooms by the day, week or longer. Whether you are travelling for business, looking for temporary or corporate housing, needing short-term housing during relocation, or planning a weekend gateway, we have the solution that will fit you budget.", "text": "A place where in the morning you have your corporate meeting, in the afternoon; you enjoy a coffee break with a nice French Cake. At night you are treated with are fined French / Italian cuisine with a continental buffet spiced with African influences. We pride ourselves with friendly staff and the practical touches that make being away from home easier, whether you book our rooms by the day, week or longer. Whether you are travelling for business, looking for temporary or corporate housing, needing short-term housing during relocation, or planning a weekend gateway, we have the solution that will fit you budget."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/7", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 131.54, "t": 539.5899999999999, "r": 404.8031199999999, "b": 490.63, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 223]}], "orig": "Hotel is on Mombasa Road 5 km from City Centre,  Distance from JKIA & SGR, is 11km, Wilson Airport - 3 Kms.  From Airport its take 10min to reach the hotel on expressway. Hotel taxi services are available on prior bookings.", "text": "Hotel is on Mombasa Road 5 km from City Centre,  Distance from JKIA & SGR, is 11km, Wilson Airport - 3 Kms.  From Airport its take 10min to reach the hotel on expressway. Hotel taxi services are available on prior bookings."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/8", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 131.54, "t": 481.03000000000003, "r": 409.54255999999987, "b": 393.67, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 448]}], "orig": "Hotel is equipped with total 59 different category of the rooms (Standards,  Executive ),  you will enjoy the quiet and peaceful atmosphere  surrounding the rooms,  safe and secure the place, 24 hours CCTV surveillance,  Fire protected, equipped with 2 lifts and 2 staircases,  All air-conditioning rooms with proper air ventilation, facility of Wifi, Intercom, Television, Minibar, Safe locker.  You can book the twin bed rooms as per your choice.", "text": "Hotel is equipped with total 59 different category of the rooms (Standards,  Executive ),  you will enjoy the quiet and peaceful atmosphere  surrounding the rooms,  safe and secure the place, 24 hours CCTV surveillance,  Fire protected, equipped with 2 lifts and 2 staircases,  All air-conditioning rooms with proper air ventilation, facility of Wifi, Intercom, Television, Minibar, Safe locker.  You can book the twin bed rooms as per your choice."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/9", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 131.54, "t": 364.01, "r": 405.6987200000002, "b": 302.21000000000004, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 265]}], "orig": "Standard rooms: Our Maison's are specially designed with bring windows that allow maximum lights in, they are equipped with all the la test facilities that offer practical touches to our guests and are equipped with queen-size beds, reading desk, safe and mini bar.", "text": "Standard rooms: Our Maison's are specially designed with bring windows that allow maximum lights in, they are equipped with all the la test facilities that offer practical touches to our guests and are equipped with queen-size beds, reading desk, safe and mini bar."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/10", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "chi